version_description:
NEW LEVEL PACK: Keep on popping in the New Year!
There’s no better way to ring in the new year than with a set of new levels!
– 20 new levels now & 20 more for later.
– Snowy winter scenery.
– Happy New Year!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Lunar New Year 2017!
Celebrate the Lunar New Year with new levels! No more monkeying around, It’s officially the year of the rooster. Score 1 for the birds.
– Lunar New Year theme
– 20 new levels now & 20 more on the way
– Lunar New Year sales. Check back soon!
– Minor fixes and improvements

NEW LEVEL PACK: Love is in the air!
It’s Valentine’s Day. Love is in the air. The air is in the bubbles. You know what to do :)
– Lovely Valentine’s Day theme!
– 20 new levels now, 20 for later!
– Gale visits as a guest bird!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Can’t stop the POP!
– 40 NEW levels!
– Luca visits as a guest bird!
We addressed some minor issues in order to improve the user experience. Thanks for playing, and keep popping those pigs!

NEW LEVEL PACK: 2 Years of POP!
It’s our 2 year anniversary, and we’re celebrating with new levels and a special guest.
– 40 new levels.
– Dahlia pays a visit.

NEW LEVEL PACK:
Get lucky in a brand new update, and play 40 new levels in 2 new areas!
– 2 New areas: Slumber Mill & Pork Chopped Wood!
– 40 new levels!
– Collect the Eggs to earn some nice rewards! (March 17-21)
– The Blues pop in for a visit! (March 24-27)

NEW LEVEL PACK: Danger above, danger below!
Watch your step, the ground could give way at any moment. Brave teetering towers and rickety bridges in 2 new precarious areas!
– 40 new levels!
– Gale visits as a guest bird!
– Get unlimited lives for a limited time in a special event!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Sweet Easter Treats!
Easter is here! Pop in and collect some eggs in a special event for sweet rewards, and watch out for Easter sales.
– 40 New levels!
– Willow visits as a guest bird!
– Collect eggs for awesome rewards!
– Easter sales!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Beauty and the Beast
Join a magical tale as old as time, but with slingshots, and lots of bubbles!
– New Beauty and the Beast area!
– 40 new levels.

NEW LEVEL PACK: Runaway Train
The POP train can't be stopped! Keep on rolling with new levels, events, and guests.
– 40 new levels!
– Luca visits as a guest bird!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Red Hood and his Merry Birds!
Put on those tights, and draw back your bow– er, slingshot for a quiver full of new levels!
– 40 new levels!
– The Blues pop in for a visit!
– Collect eggs for awesome rewards!
– Get unlimited lives for a limited time in a special event!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Theme Park!
Come one, Come all! Step right up for a new set of thrilling levels and plenty of chances to win prizes!
– 40 new levels!
– Collect eggs for awesome rewards!
– Get unlimited lives for a limited time in a special event!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Stargazing!
Things are looking up in an all-new star studded update with new levels and plenty of fireworks. 
– Empowered Boosts! The Fireball gets supercharged for a limited time.
– 4th of july Sales!
– 40 NEW Levels!
– Gale and Dahlia pay a visit!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Stargazing!
Things are looking up in an all-new star studded update with new levels and plenty of fireworks. 
– Empowered Boosts! The Fireball gets supercharged for a limited time.
– 4th of july Sales!
– 40 NEW Levels!
– Gale and Dahlia pay a visit!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Pigs of the Caribbean!
Traverse the crystal clear waters and remote islands in a new set of levels. Where there’s water, there’s sure to be bubbles!
– Collect eggs for awesome rewards!
– Luca visits as a guest bird!
– The Blues pop in for a visit!

NEW LEVEL PACK: The Pigamids!
Discover the secrets of Ancient Egypt in a new set of levels. But don’t get lost in the desert!
- Level blast! Celebrating the 2000th level in the game. For a limited time level 2000 is now available to everyone! Reach the target score for some awesome rewards!
- Fireball Fundays - all Fireballs will get SUPER CHARGED!
- Willow visits as a guest bird!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Cave of Wonders!
Travel through Arabian Nights with this brand new set of levels!
- 40 new levels!
- Super Fireball! The Fireball gets supercharged for a limited time!
- Collect The Eggs for awesome rewards!
- Dahlia pops in for a visit!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Blues Lagoon!
Can’t wait to escape the summer heat? Enjoy in the cool blue waters in The Blues’ secret lagoon with more levels, more special events, and more bubbles!

We addressed some minor issues in order to improve the user experience.

NEW LEVEL PACK: Blues Lagoon!
Can’t wait to escape the summer heat? Enjoy in the cool blue waters in The Blues’ secret lagoon with more levels, more special events, and more bubbles!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Mount Olympigs
It’s time to go back to school – waaaaaaay back. We’re going to Ancient Grease in two sets of all new levels.

NEW LEVEL PACK: Mount Olympigs
It’s time to go back to school – waaaaaaay back. We’re going to Ancient Grease in two sets of all new levels.

NEW LEVEL PACK: BotHAMical Gardens!
Team up with Terence and tend to his terraced garden in a tremendous update teaming with tons of new levels!

NEW LEVEL PACK: In search of Pigfoot!
As summer turns to autumn, the piggies head into the wilderness in search of a mythical beast. Pack a sweater, it’s getting chilly out there!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Camp Pork Chop!
Halloween is just around the corner! Don’t let the pigs’ spooky costumes scare you. We’ve got plenty of new levels, events and other Halloween treats to fill your goodie bag.
– 40 NEW levels in 2 areas!
– The Phantom of the POPera returns! 
– Halloween Candy Collection event!
– Piggy Puzzle event!
– NEW Halloween music!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Camp Pork Chop: Shadow Puppets!
The sun falls on Camp Porkchop and campfires envelop cast long shadows on the surrounding trees. From those shadows emerges a mysterious red visitor. Spoooooooky!
– 40 NEW levels in 2 new areas!
– Collect Halloween Candy!
– Phantom Red emerges from the shadows!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Giant Veggie Patch!
There’s just enough time for one last harvest before winter sets in, and it’s gonna be a big one. Enjoy a veritable cornucopia of new levels and events!
– 40 NEW levels in 2 areas!
Limited-time only:
– Extra challenging Piggy Puzzles!
– Play as The Blues!
– Incendiary Fireball Fundays!
– Unlimited lives event!

NEW LEVEL PACK – Thanksgiving!
Thanksgiving – a time to gather ‘round the table with loved ones, give thanks for what we have – and pig out! Did I say pig?
– 40 new Levels in the Feathered Feast and Turkey Treats! 
Limited-time only:
– Dahlia and Willow pay a visit!
– Incendiary Fireball Fundays! 
– Unlimited lives event!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Piggy Ski Resort
Play a new set of wintery levels and enjoy the frozen scenery from the safety of under your toasty blanket. 
– 40 new snowy, Xmasy levels! 
– Collect the Gifts! 
– Music for the Holidays!
– Special guest birds!
– iPhone X support, yay!

There’s no better way to ring in the new year than with a set of new levels!
– 80 new new snowy, wintery levels! 
– Collect the Gifts!
– Frosty Xmas and New Year’s offers!
– Special guest birds!
– New piggy puzzle for the New Year! 
– Happy New Year! 
– iPhone X support, yay!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Valentine’s Day 2018!
 Watch out! Pretty soon, Cupid’s arrows will be flying through the air. We’ve got plenty of Valentine’s goodies flying your way as well!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Jade Palace!
 Happy Lunar New Year! Get ready for plenty of new levels, new guests, and new events in the year of the dog!
 – 20 NEW levels every Thursday!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Blooming Fields!
 Spring has sprung! The grass is growing, flowers are blooming, bubbles are popping, and piggies are dropping. Join us for an Eastery update packed with levels, special guests, and events.
 – Play 40 NEW levels in 2 new areas!
 – See what special guests pop in for a visit!
 – Join special springtime events!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Hot Mountain Springs!
 Angry Birds POP celebrates its 3 year anniversary with a hot new update! We’re keeping it poppin’ with more fresh new levels and events.
 – NEW 3rd Anniversary Piggy Puzzle
 – 20 NEW levels every Thursday!
 – Anniversary sale – Mar 3-4!
 – More events – Unlimited lives, Super Fireballs, & more!

NEW LEVEL PACK: Four-Leaf Meadows!
Everything’s coming up GREEN – and we’re not talking about piggies. St. Patrick’s Day brings the luck o’ the Irish to everyone with new green levels and events. Ok, and piggies too…
– Levels! 40 NEW levels in 2 new areas.
– Events! Fireballs, rainbows, puzzles, & more!
